      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 147,
      "message": "Why is this code duplicated all over the place? How about adding a Util method \"decryptAppPassword(app)\" and embed the knowledge about how to decrypt a password there?  It's awful how the principle of information hiding has been so egregiously ignored here, and every single module that needs a password has to know what decryption algorithm is required.  Please consider refactoring.",
